<subSubSection type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageNumber="456">
diagnosis A member of the 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:33744" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Pheidole" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pheidole flavens Roger" lsidName-HNS="Pheidole flavens Roger" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="456" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavens">flavens</taxonomicName>
group similar to 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:33875" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Pheidole" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pheidole minutula Mayr" lsidName-HNS="Pheidole minutula Mayr" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="456" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minutula">minutula</taxonomicName>
but the queen much smaller, close in size to the worker caste of 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:33875" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Pheidole" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pheidole minutula Mayr" lsidName-HNS="Pheidole minutula Mayr" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="456" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minutula">minutula</taxonomicName>
